<i>The shares of the major
financial stocks plummeting.</i>

01:21:40.325 --> 01:21:42.919
<i>It's triggering a major sell-off
in the markets.</i>

01:21:43.028 --> 01:21:44.290
<i>The damage, widespread.</i>

