01:21:50.969 --> 01:21:52.368
<i>You can hear the hollering
on the floor.</i>

01:21:52.471 --> 01:21:55.406
<i>We're down 260,
literally in a split second.</i>

01:21:55.507 --> 01:21:57.270
<i>Right now,
the Dow Jones Industrial Average</i>

