01:22:59.972 --> 01:23:02.270
How much are you guys thinking?

01:23:02.374 --> 01:23:04.342
At least five.

01:23:04.443 --> 01:23:06.468
I think six.

01:23:06.578 --> 01:23:09.809
Bill, I frankly think
Harry and Charlie are low.

01:23:09.915 --> 01:23:12.042
I think we're talking seven, eight.

01:23:12.184 --> 01:23:13.742
Hundred billion?

01:23:19.925 --> 01:23:21.654
Selling this to Congress
is the problem.

01:23:22.260 --> 01:23:24.626
They're going to want to know
where the money's going.

01:23:24.730 --> 01:23:26.925
They'll jawbone this to death.

01:23:29.968 --> 01:23:31.560
- Scare them.
- How?

01:23:32.471 --> 01:23:34.200
Tell them the truth.

01:23:34.806 --> 01:23:37.741
The government's got to restore confidence.

01:23:37.876 --> 01:23:40.709
If we don't stop the bleeding,
in three days,

01:23:40.812 --> 01:23:43.406
half the banks in this room
are out of business.

01:23:43.515 --> 01:23:45.881
And in five days, we're all gone.

01:23:47.719 --> 01:23:50.313
You men realize what you've done here?

01:23:52.457 --> 01:23:57.121
You are asking for the biggest bailout
in the history of this country.

01:23:58.196 --> 01:24:00.892
You're talking nationalization, Bretton.

01:24:01.733 --> 01:24:03.064
Socialism.

01:24:05.671 --> 01:24:09.402
I have fought it all my life.

01:24:10.575 --> 01:24:12.975
And if we don't get it, Bill,

01:24:13.211 --> 01:24:15.270
there won't be any history.

01:24:15.781 --> 01:24:17.146
Music stops.

01:24:18.650 --> 01:24:20.015
Ball's over.

01:24:24.056 --> 01:24:25.182
Julie?

01:24:26.958 --> 01:24:28.391
1929.

01:24:30.529 --> 01:24:33.430
It'll get worse now,
because it'll go faster.

01:24:34.266 --> 01:24:38.862
Money markets will dry up around the world
by the end of the week.

01:24:39.004 --> 01:24:41.939
ATMs will stop spitting bills.

01:24:43.508 --> 01:24:46.204
Federal Deposit Insurance will collapse.

01:24:47.112 --> 01:24:49.080
Banks will close.

01:24:49.314 --> 01:24:50.872
Mobs, panic.

01:24:54.486 --> 01:24:57.580
It's going to be the end of the world, Bill.

01:25:02.060 --> 01:25:03.084
See?

01:25:07.232 --> 01:25:08.324
Huh!

01:25:10.102 --> 01:25:11.660
All right, boys.

01:25:12.871 --> 01:25:14.964
You'll hear from us tonight.

01:25:18.777 --> 01:25:19.766
<i>What is going to happen here?</i>

01:25:19.878 --> 01:25:20.867
<i>Does government have to get involved?</i>

01:25:20.979 --> 01:25:23.379
<i>Are we potentially at a point
where we might actually lose</i>

01:25:23.482 --> 01:25:25.382
<i>the financial system as we know it?</i>

01:25:25.484 --> 01:25:27.452
<i>If the government doesn't get involved,</i>

01:25:27.552 --> 01:25:30.817
<i>there is a risk of a global meltdown
