01:25:35.360 --> 01:25:36.759
- <i>We've seen something like this.</i>
- <i>Polly, I disagree.</i>

01:25:36.862 --> 01:25:39.592
<i>You've gotta get the government to say no
in a situation like this.</i>

01:25:39.698 --> 01:25:42.394
<i>True capitalism is about
disaster and correction.</i>

01:25:42.501 --> 01:25:43.729
<i>It's a natural cycle.</i>

01:25:43.835 --> 01:25:45.302
<i>Without it, you create all kinds</i>

