01:25:47.806 --> 01:25:49.296
<i>you're going to have...</i>

01:25:49.407 --> 01:25:52.467
<i>This is something this country
hasn't experienced before.</i>

01:25:52.644 --> 01:25:54.339
<i>It's an economic Pearl Harbor.</i>

01:25:54.446 --> 01:25:56.175
<i>We got to figure out some way
to put the fire out.</i>

01:25:56.281 --> 01:25:58.374
<i>And that means government...</i>

