When I was little,

01:26:11.062 --> 01:26:13.963
I'd hear my dad in the kitchen
late at night.

01:26:15.600 --> 01:26:16.726
His case was on appeal.

01:26:19.571 --> 01:26:22.472
I'd go and sit with him.
