01:26:24.109 --> 01:26:26.304
I never knew him as a peaceful person.

01:26:28.713 --> 01:26:30.442
It always scared me.

01:26:31.550 --> 01:26:33.017
This is scary.

01:26:34.286 --> 01:26:36.151
What's going to happen?

01:26:38.390 --> 01:26:40.017
It'll be the end.

01:26:44.029 --> 01:26:46.020
Well, that's unacceptable.

01:26:47.499 --> 01:26:48.659
Why?

01:26:49.701 --> 01:26:51.362
Because I'm pregnant, Jake.

01:27:02.047 --> 01:27:03.912
- You're pregnant?
- Yeah.

